Class BayesianNetwork.Node

  • java.lang.Object
    • bn.core.BayesianNetwork.Node
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Printable
    Enclosing class:
    BayesianNetwork

    public class BayesianNetwork.Node
extends java.lang.Object
implements Printable
    Inner class representing nodes in a BayesianNetwork. Each node corresponds to a random variable, and has parent nodes, child nodes, and a conditional probability table associated with it.
